{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 72,
  "title": "第七十二章（愛己）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "民不畏威，則大威至。"
    },
    {
      "text": "無狎其所居，"
    },
    {
      "text": "無厭其所生，"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯不厭，是以不厭。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人自知，不自見，"
    },
    {
      "text": "自愛不自貴。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故去彼取此。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "威，害也。人不畏小害則大害至。大害者，謂死亡也。畏之者當愛精神，承天順地也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂心居神，當寬柔，不當急狹也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人所以生者，以有精神。託空虛，喜清靜，飲食不節，忽道念色，邪僻滿腹，為伐本厭神也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫唯獨不厭精神之人，洗心濯垢，恬泊無欲，則精神居之不厭也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自知己之得失，不自顯見德美於外，藏之於內。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自愛其身以保精氣，不自貴高榮名於世。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "去彼自見、自貴，取此自知、自愛。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
